	(text "PCB Layout: Add decoupling caps close to the IC\n\nPEDAL_OPEN is HIGH when PEDAL < SHORT_CIRCUIT\nPEDAL_SHORT is HIGH when PEDAL > OPEN_CIRCUIT\nBRAKE_OPEN is HIGH when BRAKE < SHORT_CIRCUIT\nBRAKE_SHORT is HIGH when BRAKE > OPEN_CIRCUIT\nBRAKE_APPLIED is HIGH when BRAKE > BRAKE_THRESHOLD\nPEDAL_APPLIED is HIGH when PEDAL > PEDAL_THRESHOLD"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 341.63 108.712 0)
		(effects
